@jancborchardt tells me that this is supposed to be a pull to refresh and not show the button as it is here? 
![screenshot from 2015-05-01 23 05 51](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/2122318/7438965/4c0e60fa-f06e-11e4-9fd7-a5d9a4d3c8fa.png)

I'm on Firefox 37.0.2 on Ubuntu 14.04

It would be cool if News allowed the user to subscribe to [PubSubHubbub](http://code.google.com/p/pubsubhubbub/) publishers.

This is an example of a PHP library that implements subscription to PubSubHubbub clients: https://github.com/lxbarth/PuSHSubscriber

@Raydiation @DeepDiver1975

